16-11-09

__Dependencies__

:python:
The programming language

:wxwidgets:
The gui library

:wxpython:
The glue between wxwidgets and python

:python-mdp:
No idea...

:python-opengl:
The glue between python and opengl, probably for graphs

:python-xlib:
The glue for the X windowing system and python

:swig:
SWIG is a programmer's tool designed to make it easier to use C and C++ code from other popular programming languages such as Python, Perl, Ruby, PHP, Java, and C#.

:numpy:
Library for mathematical calculations.

:pyfann:
Fast neural network library.
The pyfann python bindings to fann must be installed manually (http://www.ocztechnologyforum.com/forum/showpost.php?p=441769&postcount=8).
Download stuff here: http://leenissen.dk/fann/download.php


__Install from ubuntu__

Type the following in a shell:
sudo apt-get install python-dev python-numpy python-usb \
  python-wxgtk2.8 wx-common python-wxaddons python-mdp \
  python-opengl python-xlib swig libfann1-dev -y

